 == About ==
 
 An enhancement of concurrency in the buffer management module of Apache Derby.
 http://code.google.com/p/derby-nb/

 The fruit of this project is Nb-GCLOCK; a non-blocking buffer management scheme 
 based on a lock-free variant of the GCLOCK page replacement algorithm.
 
 Please find the detail in the following paper: 
 Makoto Yui, Jun Miyazaki, Shunsuke Uemura and Hayato Yamana: 
 ``Nb-GCLOCK: A Non-blocking Buffer Management based on the Generalized CLOCK'', pp. 745-756, Proc. ICDE, March 2010.

 == Author ==

 Makoto Yui <m.yui _at_ aist.go.jp>

